OL,5, The son of a man who died after being  
OL,6, hit by a drink driver says he dreads   
OL,7, Christmas after having to switch off   
OL,8, his dad's life support on Boxing Day.  
OL,10,FRon Fealey, 82, was struck while       
OL,11,Fcrossing the street in Merthyr Tydfil  
OL,12,Fon Christmas Eve 2022.                 
OL,14,FHis son Mike urged people not to get   
OL,15,Fbehind the wheel after drinking or if  
OL,16,Fthey had taken drugs.                  
OL,18,FKatrina Mahoney, 34, was given a       
OL,19,Ffive-year jail sentence after failing  
OL,20,Fto stop at the scene of the crash.     
